   "source": [
    "# SR-MoE Training Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "**SR-MoE** = Sparse Routing Mixture-of-Experts with:\n",
    "1. **Popcode VQ codebook** — discrete codeword selection instead of softmax\n",
    "2. **Ring attractor** — path-dependent routing state (grid-cell-like)\n",
    "3. **Adversarial diversity regularization** — prevents code collapse\n",
    "\n",
    "Run all cells in sequence. Training logs print inline."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Setup: install deps and add project to path\n",
    "import subprocess\n",
    "subprocess.run(['pip', 'install', 'numpy', 'torch', '--quiet'], check=True)\n",
    "\n",
    "import sys, os\n",
    "# Mounted workspace is at /workspace\n",
    "PROJECT_DIR = '/workspace'\n",
